%% Diagram: Two Phase Upload Media Upload Returns Immediately With Media Id Post Creation Tr
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant GW as Gateway
    participant US as Upload
    participant IMG as Processor
    participant S3
    participant CDN
    participant PS as Post

    C->>GW: POST /upload
    GW->>US: forward
    US->>US: validate
    US->>S3: store original
    US->>IMG: process

    par Parallel
        IMG->>IMG: 1080p
        IMG->>IMG: 640p
        IMG->>IMG: 320p
        IMG->>IMG: 150p thumb
        IMG->>IMG: filter
    end

    IMG->>S3: variants
    IMG->>CDN: warm cache
    US-->>C: 200 {media_id}

    Note over C: caption + tags
    C->>GW: POST /posts
    GW->>PS: create
    PS->>PS: fan-out
    PS-->>C: 201 {post_id}
